{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"File.File()","mdn_url":"/pl/docs/Web/API/File/File","locale":"pl","native":"Polski","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/File\"><code>File</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><em><code>File()</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Własności</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/File/lastModified\"><code>lastModified</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/File/lastModifiedDate\"><code>lastModifiedDate</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/File/name\"><code>name</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/File/type\"><code>type</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/File/webkitRelativePath\"><code>webkitRelativePath</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Inheritance:</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>Konstruktor <code><strong>File()</strong></code>&nbsp;tworzy nową instancję obiektu <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/File\"><code>File</code></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"składnia","title":"Składnia","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">File(bity, nazwa [, opcje]);</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"Parameters","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"bity\"><em>bity</em></dt>\n <dd><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Array\"><code>Array</code></a> (Tablica) obiektów&nbsp;<a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer\"><code>ArrayBuffer</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/TypedArray\"><code>ArrayBufferView</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> lub&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> — albo miks takich obiektów. Zawartość pliku jest zakodowana w UTF-8.</dd>\n <dt id=\"nazwa\"><em>nazwa</em></dt>\n <dd>Obiekt {domxref(\"USVString\")}} reprezentujący nazwę pliku albo ścieżkę do niego.</dd>\n <dt id=\"opcje\"><em>opcje</em>&nbsp;<span class=\"badge inline optional\">Optional</span></dt>\n <dd>Obiekt opcji, który zawiera opcjonalne atrybuty pliku. Dostępne są następujące możliwości:\n <ul>\n  <li><code>type</code>: (typ) - Obiekt&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> reprezentujący typ MIME zawartości pliku. Domyślnie <code>\"\".</code></li>\n  <li><code>lastModified</code>: (ostatnio modyfikowany) Liczba reprezentująca liczbę milisekund pomiędzy Unix time epoch i datą ostatniej modyfikacji pliku. Domyślnie - wartość&nbsp;<a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/now\"><code>Date.now()</code></a>.</li>\n </ul>\n </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"przykład","title":"Przykład","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> plik <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">File</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">\"foo\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"foo.txt\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">type</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"text/plain\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specyfikacje","title":"Specyfikacje","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Komentarz</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/FileAPI/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"The 'File API' specification\" rel=\" noopener\">File API</a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">Working Draft</span></td>\n   <td>Podstawowa definicja</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Kompatybilność między przeglądarkami","id":"kompatybilność_między_przeglądarkami","isH3":false,"query":"api.File.File","dataURL":"/pl/docs/Web/API/File/File/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\">\n\n\n<p></p><p></p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"zobacz_także","title":"Zobacz także","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader\"><code>FileReader</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Składnia","id":"składnia"},{"text":"Przykład","id":"przykład"},{"text":"Specyfikacje","id":"specyfikacje"},{"text":"Kompatybilność między przeglądarkami","id":"kompatybilność_między_przeglądarkami"},{"text":"Zobacz także","id":"zobacz_także"}],"summary":"Konstruktor File() tworzy nową instancję obiektu File.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"File()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"File()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"File()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"File.File()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"File.File()","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"pl/web/api/file/file","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pl/web/api/file/file/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web","title":"Technologie Internetowe dla developerów"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/API","title":"Lista Web API"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/API/File","title":"File"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/API/File/File","title":"File.File()"}],"pageTitle":"File.File() - Lista Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}